trans-unit.source: Represents a security token that is based upon an X.509 certificate.
trans-unit.target: 表示 X.509 憑證為基礎的安全性權杖。

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 所使用的資源全部釋出<xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken"> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: Call the Dispose method when you are finished using the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>.
trans-unit.target: 當您完成使用<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>呼叫 Dispose 方法

trans-unit.source: The Dispose method leaves the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: Dispose 方法會使<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>中無法使用的狀態。</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>

trans-unit.source: After calling the Dispose method, you must release all references to the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: 在呼叫 Dispose 方法之後，您必須釋放所有參考<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>讓記憶體回收行程可以回收記憶體的<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>所佔用。</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call Dispose before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > 永遠呼叫 Dispose 之後，再放開您的最後一個參考至<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>。</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: 否則，它所使用的資源將不會釋放直到記憶體回收行程呼叫<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>物件的`Finalize`方法。</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether the key identifier for this instance is equal to the specified key identifier.
trans-unit.target: 傳回值，指出這個執行個體的金鑰識別碼是否等於指定的金鑰識別碼。

trans-unit.source: The MatchesKeyIdentifierClause method matches criteria in the X.509 certificate in the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken.Certificate%2A> property based on the type of the `keyIdentifierClause` parameter.
trans-unit.target: MatchesKeyIdentifierClause 方法比對準則中的 X.509 憑證中<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken.Certificate%2A>屬性根據類型`keyIdentifierClause`參數。</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken.Certificate%2A>

trans-unit.source: The following table details what is matched.
trans-unit.target: 下表詳細說明符合的項目。

trans-unit.source: |Key identifier clause type|What is matched| |--------------------------------|---------------------| |<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509IssuerSerialKeyIdentifierClause>|The value of the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2.IssuerName%2A> property and the issuer serial number returned from the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate.GetSerialNumber%2A> method.| |<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509RawDataKeyIdentifierClause>|The data returned from the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate.GetRawCertData%2A> method.| |<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SubjectKeyIdentifierClause>|The subject key identifier extension in the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2.Extensions%2A> property is matched.| |<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509ThumbprintKeyIdentifierClause>|The thumbprint that is returned by the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate.GetCertHash%2A> method.|
trans-unit.target: |金鑰識別碼子句型別 |符合的項目 | |--------------------------------|---------------------| |<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509IssuerSerialKeyIdentifierClause>|<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate.GetSerialNumber%2A>方法所傳回的值<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2.IssuerName%2A>屬性和簽發者序號。 | |<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509RawDataKeyIdentifierClause>|從<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate.GetRawCertData%2A>方法傳回的資料。 | |<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SubjectKeyIdentifierClause>|<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2.Extensions%2A>屬性中的主體金鑰識別碼延伸符合。 | |<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509ThumbprintKeyIdentifierClause>|所傳回的指紋<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate.GetCertHash%2A>方法。 |</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate.GetCertHash%2A> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509ThumbprintKeyIdentifierClause> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2.Extensions%2A> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SubjectKeyIdentifierClause> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate.GetRawCertData%2A> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509RawDataKeyIdentifierClause> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2.IssuerName%2A></xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate.GetSerialNumber%2A> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509IssuerSerialKeyIdentifierClause>

trans-unit.source: Gets the cryptographic keys associated with the security token.
trans-unit.target: 取得與安全性權杖相關聯的密碼編譯金鑰。

trans-unit.source: Use the SecurityKeys property to set the cryptographic keys for this security token to protect a SOAP message.
trans-unit.target: 若要設定的密碼編譯金鑰來保護 SOAP 訊息的這個安全性權杖使用 SecurityKeys 屬性。

trans-unit.source: The keys can be used, among other things, to digitally sign or encrypt SOAP messages.
trans-unit.target: 索引鍵可用，以及其他項目，來數位簽署或加密 SOAP 訊息。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601> of type <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SecurityKey"></xref> that contains the set of keys associated with the security token.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601>型別的<xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SecurityKey"> </xref> ，其中包含與安全性權杖相關聯的索引鍵的集合。
